snippet.title: Honor of Kings: World - Official Unreal Engine Gameplay Trailer 4K version（with new subtitles）
snippet.description:
Honor of Kings: World, a new open-world title presented by TiMi Studio Group and supported on multiple platforms, is officially revealed! Get ready to embark on a fantasy journey in a world of discovery, wonder and adventure.#HoKWorld

Follow us on Youtube & Twitter
